V0155_01_00_00_0.text:
I'm the Supreme King.
And I will rule this world.

V0155_01_00_01_0.text: I'll go where my power leads me.

V0155_01_00_02_0.text: To defeat the darkness, I must become the darkness.

V0155_01_00_03_0.text: I can easily defeat you, but I prefer to savor your demise.

V0155_01_00_04_0.text:
You dare challenge me?
You'll pay for your insolence.

V0155_01_00_05_0.text: When the strong devour the weak, power is everything.

V0155_01_00_06_0.text:
You ran from me once.
What makes you think you won't again?

V0155_03_00_00_0.text: You are powerless against my absolute might.

V0155_03_00_04_0.text: The real fight is only getting started.

V0155_03_00_05_0.text: I haven't shown my true strength yet.

V0155_05_00_00_0.text: When power is everything, I need the darkness to win!

V0155_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card.

V0155_10_00_02_0.text: Allow me to show you this.

V0155_11_01_00_0.text: I summon a monster in Defense Position.

V0155_16_00_01_0.text: With this, your existence is over.

V0155_21_00_01_0.text: No matter what you try, it will only end in your defeat.

V0155_21_00_03_0.text: Show me how strong you really are.

V0155_21_00_05_1.text: I didn't expect you to Duel so well.

V0155_28_00_00_0.text:
Don’t be mad.
You brought this destruction upon yourself.

V0155_28_00_01_0.text: This victory proves that my way is right!

V0155_28_00_02_0.text: Since you lost, everything you stand for is meaningless.

V0155_28_00_03_0.text: I must become the darkness to conquer this world.

V0155_28_00_04_0.text: There is no power that can defeat the darkness!

V0155_28_00_05_0.text:
You're no hero.
You're just another one of my victims.

V0155_29_00_00_0.text:
The darkness...
...in my heart...
...is still here...

V0155_29_00_01_0.text:
This can't be right...
You can't be stronger than me...

V0155_29_00_02_0.text: How did you defeat my infinite power...

V0155_29_00_03_0.text: How were you able to do this...

V0155_33_00_00_0.text: I'll show you what real power feels like!

V0155_33_00_01_0.text: The souls I stole will share their power with me!

V0155_33_00_02_0.text: The darkness in my heart is the source of my strength!

V0155_30_00_00_0.text: I'm not scared to Duel alone.

V0155_30_00_01_0.text: No one can escape the darkness that lurks in their hearts.

V0155_34_00_00_0.text: That mistake will lead to your demise.

V0155_34_00_01_0.text: There's no truth in a single word you say.

V0155_34_00_02_0.text: I have no time for cowards who don't want to fight.

V0155_34_00_03_0.text: You can't stop me - you're nothing more than a speed bump.

V0155_34_00_04_0.text:
What's wrong?
The Duel has only begun.

V0155_34_00_06_0.text: I need the darkness to conquer this world.

V0155_34_00_07_0.text: Let your hate fuel your strength.

V0155_34_00_08_0.text: I didn't expect you'd Duel so well.

V0155_32_00_01_0.text:
Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links
Feel the power of the shadows!

V0155_35_00_00_0.text:
I am the Supreme King.

V0155_35_00_01_0.text: My power will lead me to my destiny.
